title: DBM - Dragon Ball Multiverse 01-48 (ongoing)
description:
http://www.dragonball-multiverse.com/

Dragon Ball Multiverse (DBM) is a free online comic, made by a whole team of fans. It's our personal sequel to DBZ. 

Dragon Ball Multiverse, or for short, ("DBM") a sequel of the manga, is a free online dojinshi (fan made comic in Japanese) (manga created by non-professionals, using a universe and characters which are not theirs), made by Salagir and Gogeta Jr, from France. Salagir is the author and co-creator of the Dragon Ball Multiverse fan comic. Gogeta Jr. is the main artist and co-creator of the fan comic of DragonBall Multiverse.

I found difficulty reading it online since I wanted to easily access it through phone or tablet so I found a way grab the pages and organize them as cbr files

This torrent contains DBM chapter 49 only partially

I would like to encourage anyone who enjoys this comic book to visit 
http://www.dragonball-multiverse.com/
and buy some of their products as they rekindled the child in me with joy
